overview: This series gets you up close with the worlds most breathtaking adult actresses. Featured cover girl Sybil is a college student travelling abroad, whose polyamorous hosts make her a once-in-a-lifetime proposal. Will this striking young woman accept an adventure with an experienced older man? Venera Maxima, Gizelle Blanco, Cayenne Klein, and Addie Andrews are all here, all natural, and about to blow you away.
title: Natural Beauties 18
